Welcome to Vancouver
ADDRESS 4911 Moss Street, Vancouver
HOME PHONE NUMBER 778-847-8502
Hello! Welcome to our home. We are so glad you decided to stay here, and we
hope you have a great time in Vancouver.
We are happy to share our special getaway with you and truly hope you get to
enjoy it as much as we do. The views of the Stawamus Chief Hike in the morning are
spectacular, and there are some fantastic restaurants and breweries in the
neighborhood. Our favorite is Como Taperia.
This book contains information about the house and area to help you enjoy your
stay. You should find everything that you need, but if you have a question that isn’t
covered in here, please do get in touch by phone and let me know how we can
help.
We have provided amenities included fresh towels, bathroom supplies and kitchen
supplies. If you need to do any laundry you have full access to the washer and
dryer.
Our community is very quiet, and we have a close relationship with our neighbors.
We ask that you respect our neighbor’s privacy and keep the noise level low during
the nighttime. We are a smoke free environment and please lock the door when
you leave.
Sincerely,
The Lee family

PROCEDURE
Checking out
We hope you enjoyed your stay here!
As a reminder, check-out is at 11 am on the day that your booking
ends.
Before you leave, could you please:
• Put all the used towels in the washer
• Empty the fridge
• Bottles and recycling bins are outside.
• Collect all garbage in bags and put it outside
• Check to make sure you didn’t leave anything behind
• Reset Thermostat to 0 please
• Lock the door
• Message us that you have checked out
We would really appreciate it if you could leave us a review to let
us know how your stay was. We love to hear from our guests!
Please travel safe and come visit us again any time you’re in
Vancouver!
